quot;image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SGEH32P1/SK_05.jpg&quot; data-crop=&quot;image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SGEH32P1/SK_05.jpg?crop=0,0,550,0&quot; data-org=&quot;image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SGEH32P1/SK_05.jpg&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;content-block full-bleed-light-center-text&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;wrapper&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;content&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;default-content&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;visuals&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;images&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;img class=&quot;img-responsive&quot; alt=&quot;phu-kien-dong-ho&quot; src=&quot;image/catalog/products/2014/PK_Seiko.jpg&quot; data-crop=&quot;image/catalog/products/2014/PK_Seiko_mob.jpg&quot; data-org=&quot;image/catalog/products/2014/PK_Seiko.jpg&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;', '', 'SGEH32P1', '', ''),
(1809, 1, 'SUP216P1', '<section class="content-block full-bleed-light-center-text">\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="default-content">\r\n<div class="visuals">\r\n<div class="images">\r\n<a target="_blank" href="http://www.xwatch.vn/news/bao-hiem-dong-ho-tieu-chuan-thuy-si-p2724.html"><img class="img-responsive" alt="Bao-hiem-dong-ho" src="image/catalog/products/2014/BHDH_SEIKO.jpg" data-crop="image/catalog/products/2014/BHDH_x_mob_seiko.jpg" data-org="image/catalog/products/2014/BHDH_SEIKO.jpg" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="content-block full-bleed-dark-right-text">\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="default-content">\r\n<header style="top: 10% ">\r\n<h3 class="headline">Những vi&#234;n đ&#225; lấp l&#225;nh</h3>\r\n<div class="caption">\r\n<div align="justify">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\nV&#224;nh đồng hồ được trang điểm bằng những vi&#234;n đ&#225; Swarovski - loại đ&#225; sử dụng l&#224;m kim cương nh&#226;n tạo - với m&#224;u sắc, size, gi&#225;c cắt, độ cứng v&#224; độ s&#225;ng đạt đến mức ho&#224;n hảo. Khiến bạn thực sự nổi bật với chiếc đồng hồ tr&#234;n tay.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class="visuals">\r\n<div class="images">\r\n<img class="img-responsive" alt="Lich-su-olypianus" src="image/catalog/products/2014/seiko_bg.jpg" data-crop="image/catalog/products/2014/seiko_bg_mob.jpg" data-org="image/catalog/products/2014/seiko_bg_bg.jpg" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="content-block full-bleed-dark-right-text">\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="default-content">\r\n<header style="top:15%; margin-top:\r\n0px;color:#292929;width:50%">\r\n<h3 class="headline">Trang sức d&#224;nh cho ph&#225;i nữ</h3>\r\n<div class="caption">\r\n<div align="justify">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\nL&#224; sự kết hợp giữa vẻ đẹp quyến rũ của m&#243;n đồ nữ trang v&#224; nghệ thuật chế t&#225;c đồng hồ đặc biệt, chiếc &#8230; thực sự l&#224; thứ đồ trang sức đầy nữ t&#237;nh v&#224; duy&#234;n d&#225;ng.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class="visuals">\r\n<div class="images">\r\n<img class="img-responsive" alt="" src="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_01.jpg" data-crop="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_01.jpg?crop=0,0,550,0" data-org="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_01.jpg" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="content-block full-bleed-dark-text">\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="default-content">\r\n<header style="top: 10%;\r\nwidth:50%;margin-left:\r\n15px;">\r\n<h3 class="headline">Quyến rũ mặt Ovan </h3>\r\n<div class="caption">\r\n<div align="justify">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\nMặt Ovan c&#225;ch điệu lu&#244;n l&#224; mặt số ưa th&#237;ch của những qu&#253; b&#224;. Với vẻ quyến rũ thường thấy c&#249;ng n&#233;t đẹp qu&#253; ph&#225;i từ c&#225;c v&#242;ng đ&#225; Swarovski đ&#227; khiến bao tr&#225;i tim thổn thức.\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class="visuals">\r\n<div class="images">\r\n<img class="img-responsive" alt="" src="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_02.jpg" data-crop="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_02.jpg?crop=580,0,1099,0" data-org="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_02.jpg" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="content-block full-bleed-dark-right-text">\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="default-content">\r\n<header style="top: 15%; margin-top: 0px;\r\ncolor: #292929; width: 50%;">\r\n<h3 class="headline">Khả năng chống nước ho&#224;n hảo</h3>\r\n<div class="caption">\r\n<div align="justify">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>Bạn c&#243; thể thoải m&#225;i sử dụng SUP216P1&nbsp;trong điều kiện h&#224;ng ng&#224;y: Đi mưa, rửa tay m&#224; kh&#244;ng lo đồng hồ bị v&#224;o nước với mức Water Resistant 30m<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class="visuals">\r\n<div class="images">\r\n<img class="img-responsive" alt="" src="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_03.jpg" data-crop="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_03.jpg?crop=0,0,550,0" data-org="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_03.jpg" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="content-block full-bleed-dark-text">\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="default-content">\r\n<header style="top: 15%;\r\nwidth:45%;margin-left: 15px;">\r\n<h3 class="headline">Vẻ đẹp dịu d&#224;ng v&#224; nữ t&#237;nh </h3>\r\n<div class="caption">\r\n<div align="justify">\r\n<p>Thiết kế g&#243;c cạnh c&#225; t&#237;nh kết hợp c&#249;ng những vi&#234;n đ&#225; Swarovski  lấp l&#225;nh đ&#227; tạo n&#234;n 1  vẻ đẹp rất kh&#225;c cho chiếc SUP216P1&nbsp;Vẻ đẹp dịu d&#224;ng m&#224; nữ t&#237;nh.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class="visuals">\r\n<div class="images">\r\n<img class="img-responsive" alt="" src="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_04.jpg" data-crop="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_04.jpg?crop=550,0,1099,0" data-org="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_04.jpg" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="content-block full-bleed-dark-right-text">\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="default-content">\r\n<header style="top:15%; margin-top:\r\n0px;color:#292929;width:50%">\r\n<h3 class="headline">Những v&#242;ng tay duy&#234;n d&#225;ng</h3><div class="caption">\r\nBạn muốn 1 chiếc đồng hồ nữ t&#237;nh v&#224; dịu d&#224;ng giống như 1 chiếc v&#242;ng tay bạn đeo h&#224;ng ng&#224;y? SUP216P1&nbsp;ch&#237;nh l&#224; lựa chọn d&#224;nh cho bạn.<p><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class="visuals">\r\n<div class="images">\r\n<img class="img-responsive" alt="" src="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_05.jpg" data-crop="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_05.jpg?crop=0,0,550,0" data-org="image/catalog/products/2015/content_seiko/SUP216P1/SK_05.jpg" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="content-block full-bleed-light-center-text">\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="default-content">\r\n<div class="visuals">\r\n<div class="images">\r\n<img class="img-responsive" alt="phu-kien-dong-ho" src="image/catalog/products/2014/PK_Seiko.jpg" data-crop="image/catalog/products/2014/PK_Seiko_mob.jpg" data-org="image/catalog/products/2014/PK_Seiko.jpg" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', '', 'SUP216P1', '', '');
